g.text: Simple Item Crate Controller Sequence Diagram
Create a new Crate, Add Items
Print it over a physical (real) box
Registration Process with QR Code (from Anonymous to User)
Scan a QR Code over a box
Get SICC-API endpoint url, Admin Enrollment Token, Crate UUID
Register user and generates API Key
User is registered (can access API read/write)
After QR Code Scan and Registration Successful
Registration Process with Admin-Generated API Key (from Anonymous to User)
Sends SICC-API host URL and User's API Key
User is registered (can access API read/write)
